    <section id="about" class="about section py-5">
      <div class="container">

        <div class="row gy-4">

          <div class="col-lg-6 content" data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-delay="100">
            <p class="who-we-are">Who We Are</p>
            <h3>The Ultimate Hub for Books, Publishing & Dialogue
</h3>
            <p class="fst-italic">
            At Qaro2a, we are a premier literary hub shaping the future of reading. As a dynamic podcast, insightful book reviewer, and forward thinking publisher, we are dedicated to championing books and empowering the entire literary ecosystem. Through engaging discussions and strategic support, we bridge the gap between creative authors and passionate readers.
            </p>
            <ul>
              <li><i class="bi bi-check-circle"></i> <span>Leading Podcast & Reviews: Decoding stories and analyzing books with a modern, engaging approach.</span></li>
              <li><i class="bi bi-check-circle"></i> <span>Publishers of Fresh Voices: Bringing impactful contemporary literature to light and supporting authors.</span></li>
              <li><i class="bi bi-check-circle"></i> <span>Advocates for the Reading Community: Fostering a powerful, supportive ecosystem for every book lover.</span></li>
            </ul>
          </div>

          <div class="col-lg-6 about-images" data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-delay="200">
            <div class="row gy-4">
              <div class="col-lg-6">
